    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/f959088a832a621c647399812c769c91.avif?t=1770863700\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/db9f06605d579e59a9a8dfdd3456950e.avif?t=1770863700\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的手绘画风能够展示出建筑的每一个细节，色彩的精心搭配让每一座建筑物都辨识度十足，随着城镇扩展，会有越来越多的小人入住，建造你的卡牌小镇吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/37b7b5ad938219e99359126ff62047c3.poster.avif?t=1770863700\" width=610 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/37b7b5ad938219e99359126ff62047c3.webm?t=1770863700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/37b7b5ad938219e99359126ff62047c3.mp4?t=1770863700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/9815d094d997a090b03f656cf2297c61.avif?t=1770863700\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏独特的动画，让每一座建筑物的搭建都惊喜满满，翻转、折叠，楼房盖成！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/89ee4bdf8545464b4e2097532f131cab.poster.avif?t=1770863700\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/89ee4bdf8545464b4e2097532f131cab.webm?t=1770863700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/89ee4bdf8545464b4e2097532f131cab.mp4?t=1770863700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/29b2cde86e88cbfc43cd1578b95e2cf6.avif?t=1770863700\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有超过100种建筑物和能力卡，9种不同模式供你游玩，同时各种随机事件、节日、任务会让你扩建之旅充满未知！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/0a20d66068ebb7993b2aab5a15a51344.poster.avif?t=1770863700\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/0a20d66068ebb7993b2aab5a15a51344.webm?t=1770863700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/0a20d66068ebb7993b2aab5a15a51344.mp4?t=1770863700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/9eb0f15b93095f5ea5fc96f6391c343d.avif?t=1770863700\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《卡牌城镇》里有丰富的局外成长元素，随着每一局的游玩，你都会解锁新内容，新建筑、新模式、新的随机事件。你的扩建经验会帮助你更好的管理建筑物、但也会有更多的随机事件等着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/ef1a4147f331a7c1201118128b34cb0c.poster.avif?t=1770863700\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/ef1a4147f331a7c1201118128b34cb0c.webm?t=1770863700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198070/extras/ef1a4147f331a7c1201118128b34cb0c.mp4?t=1770863700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
